{"id":"3700","user":{"id":"206348","nickname":"Monica老莫","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/Fjln215RiKU5IjvGRd-KqQiJh8AL?attname=","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【你敢说，我就敢写】","content":"<p>大家知道，我是Monica，活泼可爱的老莫。（好套路的样子）</p>\n<p>我的小说自从上了推荐榜后，老莫同志就日夜思想如何写好小说。</p>\n<p>现在，我终于想到了一个改进小说的办法。</p>\n<p>1.欢迎大家来找Bug（什么都可以，剧情，词语等等）</p>\n<p>2.如果你有什么好办法，请在此帖说。</p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">3.如果你想让老莫把你写进小说里，可以在此帖回复老莫！！！！！！！！！！</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">现在，老莫需要几个新角色：</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">5个正派，3个反派</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">如果你想让老莫知道你想要“跑”进小说里，请在下帖回复</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">格式：</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">我想当 派（空格中填在”正“或”反“）</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">我长得.......</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">我 岁（空格中填你的岁数）</font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">那就大功告成了！！！！！！！！！！</font></p>\n<p><br></p>","board_id":"7","board_name":"灌水池塘","updated_at":1493726027,"created_at":1493466584,"n_views":111,"n_replies":22,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}